    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "Rep. Jimmy Gomez: \u201c[Trump] really never had an idea of what he wanted to accomplish. He said it was about the ballistic missiles that can reach the homeland, but those ballistic missiles are not gonna reach the homeland for at least 10 years\u2026 they don\u2019t have those capabilities.\u201d",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619481052842593566",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T23:18:14+00:00",
      "type": "video_caption"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "He thought Trump was innocent regarding the Epstein files, but he changed his mind...",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619447523031158047",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T21:08:01+00:00",
      "type": "video_caption"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "Let\u2019s talk about the war in Iran\u2026",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619392902258543902",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T17:36:03+00:00",
      "type": "video_caption"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "Don Lemon got arrested for literally reporting the news. Trump is trying to eliminate the first amendment. He\u2019s arresting journalists. Threatening licenses. And intimidating news organizations that don\u2019t provide the coverage he likes. It\u2019s all broken down in our new episode \u2014 out now.",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619388168709754142",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T17:17:44+00:00",
      "type": "video_caption"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "This administration is bad for everyone, and there is no better indication of that than the war we\u2019re in\u2026",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619373753713102110",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T16:21:45+00:00",
      "type": "video_caption"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "He\u2019s just saying it out loud\u2026",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619362562584481054",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T15:38:23+00:00",
      "type": "video_caption"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "don-lemon",
      "voiceName": "Don Lemon",
      "platform": "tiktok",
      "text": "This interview was in October of 2024\u2026 Is the economy better now under Trump?",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.tiktok.com/@donlemon/video/7619328542102277407",
